snippet.title: *UPDATED* Timeline Between Johnny Depp And Amber Heard!
snippet.description:
💙 UPDATED Timeline Between Johnny Depp And Amber Heard Drama 
Johnny Depp and Amber Heard began their journey as co-stars on a film set back in 2009. According to Entertainment Tonight, Depp and Heard first met at the Rum Diary's photoshoot in October 2009, where they were acting as each other’s love interests. Even though the movie didn’t do well and could not win many hearts, it did serve as the origination of a love affair that is way too interesting to be true.
A few years later, the two finally started dating in 2012 after Depp and his long-time partner, Vanessa Paradis, called it quits. Depp addressed the breakup in a July 2013 interview in Rolling Stone, where the actor said that “relationships are very difficult.”
Depp didn’t mention Heard in the Rolling Stone piece, which was pretty standard for him and Heard as they continued to stay private about their relationship until they made their first appearance as a couple at the 7th Annual Heaven Gala in January 2014.
